quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  24,21,ae momino! shetan ke qadmon par nah chalna. aur jo shakhs shetan ke qadmon par chalay ga to shetan to be hiyai ( ki baatein ) aur buray kaam hi betaye ga. aur agar tum par khuda ka fazl aur is ki meharbani nah hoti to 1 shakhs bhi tum mein pak nah ho sakta. magar khuda jis ko chahta hai pak kardaita hai. aur khuda suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  24,22,"aur jo log tum mein sahib fazl ( aur sahib ) wusat hain, woh is baat ki qasam nah khayen ke rishta daaron aur mohtajon aur watan chore jaane walon ko kuch kharch paat nahi den ge. un ko chahiye ke maaf kar dein aur dar guzar karen.kiya tum pasand nahi karte ke khuda tum ko bakhash day? aur khuda to bakhsnay wala meharban hai"
  24,23,jo log parhaizgaar aur buray kamon se be khabar aur imaan daar aurton par badkaari ki tohmat lagatay hain un par duniya o akhrat ( dono ) mein laanat hai. aur un ko sakht azaab hoga
  24,24,( yani qayamat ke roz ) jis din un ki zubanain haath aur paon sab un ke kamon ki gawahi den ge
  24,25,is din khuda un ko ( un ke aamaal ka ) poora poora ( aur ) theek badla day ga aur un ko maloom hojaye ga ke khuda barhaq ( aur haq ko ) zahir karne wala hai
  24,26,napak aurtain napak mardon ke liye aur napak mard napak aurton ke liye. aur pak aurtain pak mardon ke liye. aur pak mard pak aurton ke liye. yeh ( pak log ) un ( badgoiyon ) ki baton se buri hain ( aur ) un ke liye bakhshish aur naik rozi hai
  24,27,momino! apne gharon ke siwa dosray ( logon ke ) gharon mein ghar walon se ijazat liye aur un ko salam kiye baghair daakhil nah howa karo. yeh tumahray haq mein behtar hai ( aur hum ) yeh nasiyaat is liye karte hain ke shayad tum yaad rakho
